findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward and _getCurrentSupply use loops to find and remove addresses from the _excluded list and evaluate total supply, respectively, which can lead to OUT_OF_GAS exceptions if there is a long excluded addresses list.

findings.title: Liquidity locking details not provided by the team
findings.description: The liquidity locking details were not provided by the development team.
